               <t:birth when="1522"/>
               <t:floruit from="1540" to="1559">
                  Galāwdewos became emperor at the age of 18 in <t:date>1540</t:date>.
                  His reign was marked by a successful struggle against <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1522Ahmadb">ʾAḥmad b. ʾIbrāhīm al-Ġāzī</t:persName>.</t:floruit>
               <t:death when="1559" evidence="internal">He died on <t:date>23 March 1559</t:date>, in battle with <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7623NurbM">Nūr b. Muǧāhīd</t:persName>.</t:death>
               <t:residence/>
               <t:nationality type="Ethiopia"/>
               <t:faith type="EOTC"/>
            </t:person>
            
            
            
            
